data.description: 3.0% VA Loan may be assumable for qualified buyers! Looking for a home to grow with you? Stop your search! This 4 Bedroom, 3 full Bath home has all the space you need. Perfectly located on a corner lot in the Vandalia Hills neighborhood, it has been upgraded with bamboo hardwood flooring throughout the main and upper levels along with brand new granite in the kitchen! The furnace and water heater are also brand new within the past year. When you make your way upstairs, you'll find 2 of the large bedrooms, a full bathroom and an amazing finished room above the garage! This space could be used as a game room or made into an additional bedroom. Out back you'll find a fully fenced backyard, ready be made into your dream oasis, solar panels strategically placed to provide sustainable and renewable energy.
